{"tid":1102071,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"神預測片！拆解Trump點樣靠語言藝術KO希拉里","createTime":"2019-04-11T12:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T17:23:25.000Z","uid":235812,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ead07f6cc20790a0e9dbbbb16e4a5a2acb0decf5","tid":1102071,"uid":235812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:30:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Tf0gBajaG4o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTf0gBajaG4o&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=41f6db54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Tf0gBajaG4o</a><br />\n<br />\n套片英文版喺2016總統大選前半年拍好，主持解釋點解僅管自己唔支持Trump，但係仍然賭$1000美金佢會贏。入面探討咗佢點樣靠見人講人話、改花名等低成本贏咗總統大選，希望大家睇完之後，可以諗諗歷史會唔會喺2020年再度重演！<br />\n<br />\n之前出過套片分析Ellen DeGeneres嘅幽默，講下點樣嘅玩笑唔會得罪人之餘，仲令你得人鍾意。我成日講啲唔好笑嘅爛gag得罪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以覺得呢套片內容應該幾有用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i-DSGzs8QQE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Di-DSGzs8QQE&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=b253cf29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i-DSGzs8QQE</a><br />\n<br />\n另外之前出咗片分析點解Tesla CEO Elon Musk 雖然講野口窒窒，但係可以吸引到咁多人陪佢瘋狂加班，又發射火箭又搞太陽能又整電動車 （不過個咪好差，比人鬧爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5Qdc9Exsh4s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5Qdc9Exsh4s&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=142d91b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5Qdc9Exsh4s</a><br />\n<br />\n呢套片係源至Charisma on Command呢個幾成功嘅YouTube Channel，我同頻道主人傾好咗開中文版Channel，會有國語同埋廣東話片。如果有咩建議，歡迎留言話比我地知！"},{"pid":"7fa7266ddcb47003d3726d55e4cb790e89779831","tid":1102071,"uid":14423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T12:33:03.000Z",